reviews.text: A classic Hong Kong styled Cha Chan Teng serving the neighbourhood. The deep fried egg ball is so delicious but sad to tell that it was suspended until further notice. Other dishes are ordinary and you get what you expected with no surprise.
Love the vibe.  Very local and traditional cha chang tien
Typical HK service, traditional HK style food, not my cup of tea.
best "cha chang tang" in Sau Kei Wan, just a little bit crowded!

reviews.text: 一日不如一日👎
工作人員👍👍贊
只係座得好逼……店員態度錯

出品可以，假期要時問等位。
